<P>&nbsp&nbsp Below you will find a listing of the current bugs that are being
tracked and worked on for EverTools, as well as the status of each bug.  If
you have found a bug that is not listed on this table, please use EverBug to report it to
us ASAP so that we may fix it.  Items that are not confirmed will not have a priority, since we don't 
know whats causing them.  Bugs will stay up for about 5 days after they are fixed,
if you still get the bug after it is reported fixed, please send another report. Thanks!</P>

